    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior looks great with only minor surface scratches consistent with normal use, and the interior is clean with no major tears or stains. Mechanically, it is very solid, starts right up, and handles well on the road. It\u2019s a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality vehicle that\u2019s ready to drive immediately.",
      "price": 34000.0,
